<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The render() method of Zend_Form_Decorator_File add a progress_key to track file uploads if APC or upload_progress is available. If APC is available, the progress_key is set to APC_UPLOAD_PROGRESS. However, this value should not be hard-coded, as it is configurable in the php.ini file by the apc.rfc1867_name setting.</p>

<p>Ideally, Zend_Form_Decorator_File should read out the apc.rfc1867_name setting from the php.ini and use that value.</p>

    </div>
